Package com.plugin.copilotassistant.connection.tabby

Record Class Segments

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.plugin.copilotassistant.connection.tabby.Segments
Record Components:
prefix - The prefix string.
suffix - The suffix string.
filePath - The file path, aliased as "filepath" in JSON.
gitUrl - The Git URL, aliased as "git_url" in JSON.
declarations - The declarations associated with the segments.
relavantSnippetsFromChangedFiles - The relevant snippets from changed files, aliased as "relevant_snippets_from_changed_files" in JSON.
clipboard - The clipboard content.
public record Segments(String prefix, String suffix, String filePath, String gitUrl, Declarations declarations, RelevantSnippets relavantSnippetsFromChangedFiles, String clipboard) extends Record
